Intellectual Property Notice
------------------------------

Devil Ray is licensed under the BSD-3-Clause license
(https://opensource.org/licenses/BSD-3-Clause).

Copyrights and patents in the Devil Ray project are retained by contributors.
No copyright assignment is required to contribute to Devil Ray.

SPDX usage
------------

Individual files contain SPDX tags instead of the full license text.
This enables machine processing of license information based on the SPDX
License Identifiers that are available here: https://spdx.org/licenses/

Files  contain the following text in the license header:

    SPDX-License-Identifier: (BSD-3-Clause)

External Packages
-------------------
Devil Ray bundles its external dependencies in src/thirdparty_builtin.  These
packages are covered by various permissive licenses. See the license included
with each package for full details.
